DialogueNode.dialogue: Hey Dave, what were you about to say earlier? You seemed to have something on your mind.
Well . . . Okay. I trust you're here to help, Alex.
The other day Stan totally blew up at Sharon. He told her that she needs to stop letting her "hormones interfere with her work."
She was so embarrassed... She left early.
Thank you so much for sharing this with me, Dave. I promise, the appropriate action will be taken. You've helped a lot of people today.
Anytime. Let me know if there's anything else I can do to help. I really would like to see this office become a better place.
Me too, Dave. And it's going to be.
